        2025" calender-icon="true" movieRating="true"
        button-url="movie-detail.html" movieText="Arrival is a science fiction film directed by Denis Villeneuve, based
        on Ted Chiangnovella Story of Your Life. The movie follows linguist Dr. Louise Banks (Amy Adams) as she is
        recruited by the U.S. military to communicate with mysterious extraterrestrial beings who have arrived on Earth
        in massive, hovering spacecraft. As global tensions rise and nations scramble to interpret the aliens
        intentions, Louise works with physicist Ian Donnelly (Jeremy Renner) to decipher their complex, nonlinear
        language. The film explores themes of time, communication, and the nature of human experience, blending
        intellectual depth with emotional resonance."}}

