        button-url="movie-detail.html" movieText="The film builds tension through atmospheric cinematography, depicting
        haunting landscapes in Australia's Riverland region. Critics have praised Sarah Snook's performance but noted
        the film's reliance on familiar horror tropes, comparing it to The Babadook and Hereditary. Despite mixed
        reviews, Run Rabbit Run stands out for its exploration of motherhood, grief, and the psychological toll of
        buried memories."}}

        {{> components/widgets/movie-slider movieCard="movie-banner-3" image-path="media/chosfies.webp"
